# AI-native knowledge-first (core)

> Knowledge defines, rules enforce, AI executes, humans approve.

**Human-directed agents:** People **author or update** artifacts by directing a Cursor agent (**.cursor/rules/** + **.cursor/skills/**) so edits land in git across **`knowledge/`**, **`docs/`**, **`src/`**, and **`tests/`** тАФ humans approve; agents improve throughput.

**Official KFS (agent core):** **`.kfs/INDEX.md`** ┬╖ scenarios **`.kfs/agent/START.md`** ┬╖ runbooks **`.kfs/agent/runbooks/`** ┬╖ specs **`.kfs/specs/`** (knowledge model, architecture intent, HLD, test strategy, CI/CD).

### Document and artifact layout

| Layer | Location |
| --- | --- |
| Architecture intent | **`docs/architecture/`** тАФ how to write: **`.kfs/specs/architecture_intent_spec.md`** |
| HLD | **`docs/design/`** тАФ **`.kfs/specs/design_spec.md`** |
| Test plan | **`docs/test/`** тАФ strategy: **`.kfs/specs/test_strategy_spec.md`** |
| PRD | **`docs/prd/`** |
